title: The Archer
description:
Track 5 alert! Taylor goes deep with this song, and so do we! Anxiety, heartbeat, sadness, humpty dumpty.. Just a few things Taylor hits on with this deeply emotional track. Are we going to have do make another track 5 rankings after this episode? Probably. Amy definitely needs to think about it.
What did we miss? What would you like to see us do next? Let us know!
